Whatever had happened, Vlad sure didn't remember. Last thing, there 
was that Drake insisting about some medication...

His head felt as if it was spinning like a gauss slug, and his stomach 
felt nauseous like freebirth! He stayed there, lying on his back with 
his eyes closed and just concentrated on his breathing.
